    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood and roof, though there is no major body damage. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, but the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from a tune-up soon to address minor idling inconsistencies. It is a reliable choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that gets the job done.",
